	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"&bApplied Energistics 2&r is a mod all about Matter, Energy, and using them to take over the world. It adds arguably the &6most powerful logistics systems&r in modded Minecraft, and will be extremely helpful to learn early on."
				""
				"The mod's &bbuilt-in guide&r is extremely well put-together, and should be used as a reference for mod mechanics, and can be used as a &6substitute for this questline&r, barring recipes. You can get a copy of the guide within an &6Eccentric Tome&r obtained from the &6Useful Tools&r questline."
				""
				"{ \"text\": \"[Eccentric Tome Quest]\", \"underlined\": \"true\", \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"580C9EFE799877FB\" } }"
			]
			id: "68876BE0591604C2"
			size: 2.0d
			tasks: [{
				id: "1A58E0F2B8A15DF4"
				title: "Applied Energistics 2"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["68876BE0591604C2"]
			description: [
				"To start, you'll want to find a &bSky Stone Meteor&r. These can be found basically anywhere on the surface, and are really difficult to miss. If you can't find one, you can craft a &6Meteorite Compass&r that will lead you to one."
				""
				"Inside the meteor, you'll find a &bMysterious Cube&r. Break the Cube &7(without Silk Touch)&r, and you'll get a set of each &bInscriber Press&r needed to continue."
			]
			icon: "ae2:mysterious_cube"
			id: "1AED6BCDB038D4EB"
			rewards: [{
				id: "25207C4993BC95E2"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 20
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "31D9103D824F8E25"
				item: {
					Count: 1
					id: "itemfilters:or"
					tag: {
						RepairCost: 0
						display: {
							Name: "{\"text\":\"Main Inscriber Presses\"}"
						}
						items: [
							{
								Count: 1b
								id: "ae2:calculation_processor_press"
							}
							{
								Count: 1b
								id: "ae2:engineering_processor_press"
							}
							{
								Count: 1b
								id: "ae2:logic_processor_press"
