						]
					}
				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Getting Started"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1AED6BCDB038D4EB"]
			description: [
				"Within the Meteor, you'll also find some Budding Certus Quartz blocks. These will, similarly to Amethyst, grow crystals over time."
				""
				"However, they also have a lot of differences. Check out the Getting Started page in the AE2 Guide for more info."
			]
			id: "6AB127E31D5A414C"
