		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1AED6BCDB038D4EB"]
			description: [
				"The &bInscriber&r is a machine that will make use of &6Inscriber Presses&r and &6other materials&r to create &bprinted circuits and processors&r, which are necessary to craft many AE2 components. &cThis block requires power to operate.&r"
				""
				"You may also &6duplicate Inscriber Presses&r using an Iron Block in the Inscriber."
			]
			id: "22BBECAC2DD615CB"
			rewards: [{
