			x: 1.0d
			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1AED6BCDB038D4EB"]
			description: [
				"The &bCharger&r is a block capable of &6charging compatible items&r, as well as providing power to items that can store power. &cThis block requires power to operate.&r"
				""
				"The &6most common use&r of the Charger is to produce &bCharged Certus Quartz&r, a useful material."
