				"6AB127E31D5A414C"
			]
			description: ["By throwing &6Charged Certus Quartz, Redstone Dust, and some Nether Quartz&r into water, you can create &bFluix Crystals&r, which are extremely important in crafting many AE2 components."]
			id: "6CEEC5D9627C306E"
