		{
			dependencies: ["22BBECAC2DD615CB"]
			description: [
				"&bProcessors&r will make up a large majority of crafting components used in AE2."
				""
				"Every processor will require a piece of &6printed silicon&r, and redstone dust. The main material dictates the processor created:"
				"- &6Gold Ingots:&r Logic Processors"
				"- &6Diamonds:&r Engineering Processors"
				"- &6Certus Quartz:&r Calculation Processors"
				"Naturally, each processor's printed circuit will &6require the respective press&r."
				""
				"Silicon can be obtained by smelting &6Certus Quartz Dust&r, which can then be turned into printed silicon in the &6Inscriber&r."
			]
			id: "5A55E22C6CFF8ADA"
			rewards: [{
