		{
			dependencies: [
				"0B38F16DB41E2CB2"
				"6F1701A9FE54115B"
			]
			description: [
				"&bME Cables&r allow you to connect Devices in your Network together over a distance. They come in the &6base Fluix color, as well as the 16 Minecraft colors&r."
				""
				"Colored cables will only connect to &bother cables of the same color&r, with the exception of Fluix, which can connect to &6any color&r."
				""
				"Each variant of cable can carry a &6different amount of Channels&r:"
				"- &bNormal cables&r &7(glass, smart, and covered)&r can carry up to 8 channels."
				"- &bDense cables&r &7(smart and covered)&r can carry up to 32 channels."
				""
				"&6Smart cables&r will make their channel usage visible on the cable texture itself, and to Jade."
				""
				"&6Dense cables&r, while carrying many more Channels, &ccannot connect directly to cable subparts&r, such as Terminals. In these cases, you can &bstep down the connection&r using a normal cable."
			]
			hide_dependency_lines: true
